name: Kekius Maximus
description: $KEKIUS is a community-driven meme token inspired by the fusion of internet culture, Elon Musk’s viral persona as "Kekius Maximus," and Roman imperial aesthetics. Built on the Solana blockchain, $KEKIUS aims to redefine the meme economy with a focus on speed, scalability, and low transaction fees. It’s not just a cryptocurrency—it’s a cultural movement designed to unite meme creators, crypto enthusiasts, and degens under one banner. By blending humor, innovation, and strategic partnerships, $KEKIUS is leading the charge in the meme space, empowering its community to create, share, and build a new kind of digital empire.
